title: "Report: Amazon Considering Investment in Regional-Sports Programmer Diamond Sports Group"
text: "In a potential move that would further solidify its presence in the sports content industry
source_name: Amazon is reportedly in talks to invest in Diamond Sports Group
date: the largest regional-sports programmer in the country."

title: "Alphabet Jumped Again Today Thanks to AI -- Is the Stock a Buy?"
text: "Mega-cap tech stocks continued to post strong gains Monday. Gains for Alphabet and other big-tech players continue to be powered by competitive advantages in AI."

title: "Apple Watch interruption could fuel a revenue decline in the important December quarter"
text: "The sudden interruption in most Apple Watch sales during the all-important holiday shopping season could potentially fuel another revenue decline for the tech giant's December quarter."
